

KABAONG

   ataud, ataul, kahong sisidlang ng patay
   kabaong
   coffin, casket

   kabaong ng kamatayan
   coffin of death

   kabaong ni Kamatayan
   coffin of Death (death as a person)

   kabaong na itim
   black coffin

   itim na kabaong
   black coffin

   Another Filipino word for ‘coffin’ or ‘casket’ is ataul (ataol),
   derived from the Spanish ataúd.
